title: Legible?
content: What do you think it says?
author: alex

comments.content: If you "zoom out" the first letter could be a cap 'G'.
Ja8 -\> German: Ja acht -\> Jacht -\> Yacht

Needs working then!   
Stuart you we're right, it says JaX...   
Thankyou everyone
